  "texts": [
    "The Metaverse platform collects data from various IoT devices to ensure seamless integration across a wide range of Metaverse applications, such as healthcare, education, and smart cities.",
    "These IoT devices will employ diverse hardware, controllers, and objects to bridge the physical world with the Metaverse.",
    "Specific sensors on these IoT devices enable navigation in both the physical and virtual worlds upon connection to the Metaverse.",
    "The ability of IoT devices to perform such tasks is crucial for users to participate in Metaverse activities.",
    "Blockchain technology allows IoT devices to communicate across different networks, generating secure records of shared transactions within virtual worlds."
